[CITE@@en[<font> and style="" in HTML5]] ([[Ian Hickson]] 著, [TIME[2008-04-29 21:21:45 +09:00]] 版) <http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/public-html/2008Apr/0795.html>
([[名無しさん]])


[[#comment]]


